sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as Trainer Controller<br/>(opendatahub namespace)
    participant JobSetOp as JobSet Operator
    participant TrainingPod as Training Pod<br/>(user namespace)

    Note over User,TrainingPod: Flow 1: TrainJob Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: POST TrainJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token / Client Cert
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /validate-trainer-...-trainjob<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS, TLS (self-managed)<br/>Auth: API server client cert
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (allow/deny)
    K8sAPI-->>User: TrainJob created

    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event: TrainJob created
    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET TrainingRuntime/ClusterTrainingRuntime<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Runtime template

    Note over Controller: Plugin Framework processes:<br/>1. EnforceMLPolicy (Torch/MPI/TorchTune)<br/>2. EnforcePodGroupPolicy (Coscheduling/Volcano)<br/>3. ComponentBuilder (JobSet)

    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE JobSet CR (server-side apply)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE NetworkPolicy (RHAI)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: JobSet created

    JobSetOp->>K8sAPI: CREATE Jobs + Pods<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>JobSetOp: Pods scheduled

    Note over User,TrainingPod: Flow 2: RHAI Progression Tracking

    Controller->>K8sAPI: LIST Pods (APIReader, no cache)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Pod list (primary pod IP)

    loop Every 30s (configurable 5s-300s)
        Controller->>TrainingPod: GET /metrics<br/>28080/TCP HTTP plaintext<br/>Auth: None (NetworkPolicy enforced)
        TrainingPod-->>Controller: Metrics JSON<br/>(step, total_steps, epoch, loss, ETA)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH TrainJob annotations<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Bearer Token
    end

    Note over User,TrainingPod: Flow 3: MPI Training Setup (when MPI policy)

    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE Secret ({name}-mpi-ssh-auth)<br/>SSH key pair for inter-node auth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, TLS 1.2+
    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE ConfigMap ({name}-mpi-hostfile)<br/>Worker endpoints and slots<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, TLS 1.2+

    Note over TrainingPod: MPI Launcher pod
    participant MPIWorker as MPI Worker Pods<br/>(user namespace)
    TrainingPod->>MPIWorker: SSH connection<br/>22/TCP SSH<br/>Auth: SSH key pair from Secret
    MPIWorker-->>TrainingPod: Training results
